title: [Outlands, Rockspawn Willow]
description: Too shaded for grass or cattails, a lavender carpet of sun-dappled shadesilk blossoms covers the bank to the water's edge.  Willow leaves touching the water create a border of tiny wakes in the surface of the Rockspawn as it flows westward.
